"target":"reccdFYIq50NyxNej","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recEB3NTMbC0eDJhR","target":"recqIoG1fkaNWJ1y0","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recEB3NTMbC0eDJhR","target":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recEB3NTMbC0eDJhR","target":"recOZxrWd00qyF4Ej","label":"event"},{"source":"recEB3NTMbC0eDJhR","target":"recmXmhZt51doQu7o","label":"event"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec9gqlDMbHQjcuc0","ref":"Matt.22.1","text":"And Jesus answered and spake unto them again by parables, and said,","year":33},{"id":"recbYETNsiWDA1nKm","ref":"Matt.22.2","text":"The kingdom of heaven is like unto a certain king, which made a marriage for his son,","year":33},{"id":"recbVkENvTKHCCJFz","ref":"Matt.22.3","text":"And sent forth his servants to call them that were bidden to the wedding: and they would not come.","year":33},{"id":"reccHrg6ea6MvJRgG","ref":"Matt.22.4","text":"Again, he sent forth other servants, saying, Tell them which are bidden, Behold, I have prepared my dinner: my oxen and my fatlings are killed, and all things are ready: come unto the marriage.","year":33},{"id":"reckC1odHO5bBh68Y","ref":"Matt.22.5","text":"But they made light of it, and went their ways, one to his farm, another to his merchandise:","year":33},{"id":"recDy9eMgb7E845ll","ref":"Matt.22.6","text":"And the remnant took his servants, and entreated them spitefully, and slew them.","year":33},{"id":"recPRmjxQuvrtXQ0B","ref":"Matt.22.7","text":"But when the king heard thereof, he was wroth: and he sent forth his armies, and destroyed those murderers, and burned up their city.","year":33},{"id":"recpWdXQmJJjU2mAT","ref":"Matt.22.8","text":"Then saith he to his servants, The wedding is ready, but they which were bidden were not worthy.","year":33}]}
